rows.label: qst105903_msg001
rows.name:
What? A trade? I don't really
do that sort of thing...

rows.label: qst105903_msg002
rows.name:
...No, wait. Let me get
a better look at that.

rows.label: qst105903_msg003
rows.name:
Oh! This is it! This is exactly
the wood I was looking for!

rows.label: qst105903_msg004
rows.name:
Yeah, I needed this wood
for the interior I'm
currently working on, but...

rows.label: qst105903_msg005
rows.name:
...it's a rare material, so it
was hard to get my hands on.

rows.label: qst105903_msg006
rows.name: With this and some Puzzle Trees...

rows.label: qst105903_msg007
rows.name:
Oh, really? Then I guess
I'll ask you guys.

rows.label: qst105903_msg008
rows.name:
I heard you can often find
Puzzle Trees in Gula, around [location].

rows.label: qst105903_msg009
rows.name:
As for the number... well...
It would be a great help if you
could bring me about three.

rows.label: qst105903_msg010
rows.name: Alright, I'm counting on you!

rows.label: qst105903_msg101
rows.name:
I need three Puzzle Trees. I heard
you can find them around [location] in Gula.

rows.label: qst105903_msg102
rows.name: Sorry, but I'm counting on you!

rows.label: qst105903_msg201
rows.name: You brought them! Thanks!

rows.label: qst105903_msg202
rows.name:
With this, I can finally
finish the interior!

rows.label: qst105903_msg203
rows.name:
Yeah, you're a lifesaver! Thanks
to you, I'll make the deadline!

rows.label: qst105903_msg204
rows.name:
...Oh, right. This is a token of
my gratitude. Please take it.

rows.label: qst105903_msg205
rows.name:
I got it from an acquaintance
in Invidia, but it doesn't
really suit me.

rows.label: qst105903_msg206
rows.name:
I never wore it once, and it's just
been collecting dust in my closet.

rows.label: qst105903_msg207
rows.name:
It feels wrong to just let
it sit there, so please,
take it if you like.

rows.label: qst105903_msg208
rows.name:
I hear it's a pretty rare
item over there, so it
should be worth having.
